the mystery of san &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; is a feature-length documentary inspired by the book , the jews of san &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; , written by professor john davis , about a group of italian roman catholics in a small village , who underwent a mass conversion to judaism in fascist italy . and who over a period of twenty years of observing jewish practices , left italy and emigrated to the new state of israel in 1949 .